game.name: Elsa Find And Dress Up
game.description:
Wow! One of your favorite princesses Elsa has come with a kind of new fun and entertainment challenges. Do you want to join her and prove your love for the princess again? Join Elsa Find and Dress Up game and get ready to sort out the three puzzles in a single challenge! When you click the play button, you would notice that her room is a mess and it is really getting difficult for the princess to pick her outfits, beauty products and other accessories. Be prepared to play multiple roles single handedly! 

Your objective in this brand new dressing game is to help the princess to spot the hidden items scattered at different places in her room and then guide her to pick up the nice dress for the date. Her love is waiting for the princess outside and she has approached you for the instant help. There are three stages in this html5 princess dress up game. In the first stage, you would have to find out the items in just 15 clicks. Items may be on the dressing table, on the ground or in her wardrobe. 

In the second stage, you have to give her a lovely makeover. Give her a nice lipstick, a matching eyebrow and apply all the other beauty items to make her face glow in this dress-up simulation game! You have to dress her up with the awesome outfit in the third stage. Complete all the third stages and get ready to play the role of a fashion stylist in this one of the best girls games! Have more fun online, no download required in our dress up games for kids!
